items.title: Disney Cast Member Chronicles Wiki
items.desc: "Disney Cast Member Chronicles" is a Disney Fan-Site, that's set in Disney parks, resorts, cruise ships, Disney Stores, and destinations all over the world. Much like the kingdom keepers book series, the protagonists (Disney Park Castmembers) Solve mysterious and discover secrets after the park is closed. After dark the parks come alive, including the animatronics, some friendly, and some not so much, while a evil villain plans to take ultimate control. On this wiki we have stories, and events, so enjoy your stay!
